      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.qIIoypmTFypnmRer]{Evolutionist Adaption}</p>\n<p>By temporarily deactivating one of your augmentations, you can power new mutations and adaptations. As a swift action, you can temporarily deactivate an augmentation installed in one of your systems, losing the benefits it grants you for 1 hour (this doesn’t uninstall the augmentation). This augmentation must be of the type associated with your niche. You gain a number of MP equal to half the deactivated augmentation’s level (minimum 1 MP). Each augmentation can only be used to power this adaptation once per day.</p>"
